{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act41side", "eventName": "輓歌燃燒殆盡", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "EA-ST-2", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "羅曼史已死", "storyInfo": "高尚的紅龍回到城中。為贏得更多人的未來，她直面貪婪的紅龍，殺死她，卻也哀悼她。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你剛剛講到……是了，夏末節前夜，太陽還掛在天上的時候。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "夏末節的夜晚將連通生命與死亡，這並不是迷信，或者，它早就超出了迷信的範疇。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "塔拉的傳說中，無數偉業與慘劇都在這一夜發生，而這些傳說往往不會費心在日期上故弄玄虛。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "只要無數傳說都在這一天重合，只要塔拉人還隱約記得要在這一天慶祝豐收，點起火焰，它就不只是一個無聊的時節。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "它自身就是神話最好的注腳。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "……哦，還有，我替你故事裡的角色取些更貼切的名字，想必你也不會在意的，對嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g10_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "太陽已經西斜。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我們是還沒想好該如何見這最後一次面嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1684_1#2$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1685_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1685_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉芙希妮，你怎麼又在吃飯時躲進自己房間裡了？", "name": "冰冷的幼龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1685_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1684_1#13$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸爸生氣了嗎？", "name": "溫熱的幼龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1684_1#13$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1685_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有，不過快了。", "name": "冰冷的幼龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1685_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1684_1#14$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我現在就去——", "name": "溫熱的幼龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1684_1#14$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1685_1#22$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在你桌上的是什麼？", "name": "冰冷的幼龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1685_1#22$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1684_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒什麼！", "name": "溫熱的幼龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1684_1#12$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年幼的紅龍試圖用身體擋住姐姐的視線，但這完全是徒勞。"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她桌上放著一個小小的紙盒，裡面仔細地用棉花鋪好，上面躺著一隻已經死去，但尚有餘溫的小小羽獸。"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羽獸的腿似乎在活著的時候斷掉了，旁邊散落著硬紙做的不成功的夾板，以及幾顆麥粒。"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1684_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1685_1#22$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是每天早上都來我窗前唱歌的羽獸，不知為什麼變成了這個樣子……我想救牠，可是……", "name": "溫熱的幼龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1684_1#3$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1685_1#14$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "冰冷的幼龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1685_1#14$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1684_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "求你了，姐姐，求你去告訴爸爸，我只是不舒服，我明天會按時出現在餐桌前……我今晚就去把牠埋到院子裡。", "name": "溫熱的幼龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1684_1#2$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1685_1#22$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要放棄了嗎？", "name": "冰冷的幼龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1685_1#22$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1684_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牠已經死了啊，姐姐。", "name": "溫熱的幼龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1684_1#2$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1685_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？", "name": "冰冷的幼龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1685_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1685_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_magic_n", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紫色的火焰從羽毛間滲入羽獸已然冰冷的屍體。"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在兩人的注視之下，羽獸緩緩站了起來，斷掉的腿硬邦邦地直抵在棉花上，支撐著僵硬的軀殼。"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1684_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1685_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，你想讓牠飛起來嗎？還是唱首歌給你聽？", "name": "冰冷的幼龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1685_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1684_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不——不該是這樣的，不是的！", "name": "溫熱的幼龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1684_1#12$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1685_1#16$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "冰冷的幼龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1685_1#16$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你不想這樣，為什麼不在牠還活著的時候用你的火呢？", "name": "冰冷的幼龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1685_1#16$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1685_1#17$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的羽獸原本還可以活很久。你知道自己本不必拘泥於那些庸人的做法。", "name": "冰冷的幼龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1685_1#17$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1684_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，媽媽告訴過我，把火焰吞下去，藏起來，不要被人看到……", "name": "溫熱的幼龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1684_1#3$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1685_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有誰會看到呢？", "name": "冰冷的幼龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1685_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幼龍移開視線，不去看姐姐的眼睛，卻正好看到了僵硬地站在棉花小床上的羽獸。"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那羽獸眼中燃燒著紫火，就連略微歪著腦袋的樣子，都和姐姐一模一樣。"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "或者，我們心中都還抱著不切實際的奢望？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g6_noblelivingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐，你身上有血……你受傷了？！", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的血不多，那個大公爵派來的偵察兵的血不少。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#6$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我來幫你包紮……", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沃里克伯爵呢？", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#6", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他去……辦事。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#6"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，他一向告訴我們自己是去辦事，而你則滿足於這個字眼。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#15$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他甚至放任那個偵察兵，在自己去“辦事”的時候和你探討詩歌。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#14$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為我沒有洩漏任何跟我們的身世、跟伯爵的理想相關的訊息……", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#2"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伯爵宅第內的每個人都知道你從不說多餘的話，沃里克伯爵想確定的從來都不是這個。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#5$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#2"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，就算你放跑了偵察兵，沃里克伯爵也總有方法將他掐滅在黑暗中，而我們身上又會再多一條細細的枷鎖。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#15$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起，我……", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#2"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必道歉，道歉也是徒勞。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#15$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "往日賓朋滿座的會客廳裡空空蕩蕩，撕開繃帶的哧哧聲反倒讓空氣更顯得滯重。"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你最近很喜歡的那位西莫·威廉姆斯的詩，如果能想得起來，就幫我唸兩句吧。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高尚的紅龍在腹中搜刮能不觸怒姐姐的詩句，也許是關於塔拉的、關於戰士的，哪怕關於那些古老的傳說——"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她只想起一些與世無爭的句子。"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“大地不過是一段陌生的傳奇，結尾因不幸的偶然丟失。”", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我不過是一個吟遊詩人，只熟習森林中傳唱的知識……”", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她偷偷看向姐姐的面龐，沒看到什麼變化，於是她鼓起勇氣，繼續念誦下去。"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到整首詩都被她唸完，繃帶也打上了精緻的結，她才發現，姐姐已經在詩句的環繞下沉沉睡去。"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g13_castlebalcony", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "或者……？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，拉芙希妮，我等你很久了。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你新交的朋友們呢？那位離群的守靈人，還有活潑的遊牧民小姐？", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要有你在，阻止你們來到這裡的一切障礙應該都已經蕩然無存了。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她們已經在城裡了，但此時此刻，這是我們兩個人之間的事。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#8$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陽台上風有些刺骨，我們進到走廊裡說吧。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉布雷德的葬身之處在納斯爾紗的複製品……姐姐，你就真的這麼拘泥於重複一段並不光彩的歷史嗎？", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來你對塔拉這個名詞的理解又深了一些。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#16$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但歷史若是不重複，我們又談何將其打破呢？", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "要從外表區分我們，很難。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "只是，一旦我們之中哪一個先開了口，辨別我們姐妹就再簡單不過。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "愛布拉娜只隨著自己的興趣轉變話題，而拉芙希妮從來都是更有禮貌的那個。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她會為了一個故事的結局刨根問底——", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "別打岔，先生。我在說故事裡的人物。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g11_castlecorridor_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愛布拉娜，我很抱歉。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我很高興，你終於來赴我的約了。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跳舞？", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，跳舞。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會陪著你把那支舞跳完的，但……", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先告訴我，姐姐，上次我們見面時，你說你等不起了……究竟是怎麼回事？", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐就那樣微笑著立在長廊的盡頭，妹妹則在壁燈的陰影中握緊雙手，以為這樣就不會被對方發覺自己內心的動搖……"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可憐的孩子，她本來可以讓這場道別快一點結束的。"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你變得……虛弱了。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死火有其定數，將其散布出去，的確在一步步將你拖垮，就像當年的拉布雷德……是這樣嗎？", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來那個鬼魂的火焰與我相似，性情卻讓他和你走得更近。他真是幫了你不少的忙。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他原本只想看整個塔拉被火焰焚盡呢。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他只是在硬撐罷了……", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像你一樣。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高尚的紅龍終於走出陰影，走上前去，攙扶住看起來幾乎快站不住的姐姐……就像從前那樣。"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#6$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你終於又像很小很小的時候那樣，像你還對自己的火焰和命運一無所知時那樣，想站到我身前保護我了。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是過了很長時間了啊，拉芙希妮。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#16$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得那件事。隔壁的莫菲太太去世了，你不喜歡她，卻喜歡她靈柩中那束美麗的花……", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是你用自己的火，讓她換了個姿勢躺在棺中。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看見了花上的焦痕，覺得你會挨駡，就去跟父母說是自己做的，還花了心思，編造了把靈柩打開又關上的過程……", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結果挨了父母的一頓責駡。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可憐的爸爸媽媽連隱藏這家人的火都來不及，又怎麼會去一束花邊細細察看什麼焦痕呢？", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是啊。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是你一直退縮不前的原因嗎？", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會將漫長生活中所有的決定都歸咎於童年的某次不幸的經歷嗎？", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哈哈。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我，姐姐，告訴我一切都還來得及。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會陪你踏進堡壘下的廣場，讓人們把火焰歸還給你。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會陪你走過塔拉的原野，讓那些你有意或無意間用法術驚醒的死者安眠。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會在你仍然虛弱的時分為你唸詩，直到你睡去又醒來。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一切都還來得及，對嗎？", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信你言出必踐，你的高尚讓你無論如何都會信守承諾，拉芙希妮。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你剛剛描繪出的場景，真的會讓你自己快樂嗎？", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#15$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是說，這是只足以取悅那個連父母亡故的雪夜都還未曾經歷的拉芙希妮·都柏林的……美好的幻象？", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#15$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉芙希妮，詩是好的，愛是好的，夢是好的，但你的夢該醒了。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#15$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殺死我，這就是眼前的亂局唯一的解答，如果你真的想將其解決的話。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，戴上那頂冠冕，你將成為我，我也將成為你。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯獨這件事，我做不到。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你也可以在我死之後慢慢想。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別再猶豫了，拉芙希妮。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你決定回來見我，我們之間的選擇就只剩下一個。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#16$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐的嘴角勾起一個耐人尋味的弧度。"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來跳舞吧，拉芙希妮。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是你……一直期盼至今的舞？", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它為什麼不可以是呢？", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#16$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "妹妹閉上雙眼，對準姐姐隨時都快倒下的身軀，用雙手端起槍。"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cnstrctnck"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_daggerslow"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鋒芒貫穿紅龍的身軀，但她仍然還在那裡站著，彷彿什麼都沒發生，直到妹妹的手環上她的腰間，那身軀才緩緩倒下……"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……正如一支跳到終局的舞。"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "59_i08", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，我知道。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我早就應該知道的，姐姐。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是為什麼，為什麼偏偏要是現在？", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不然呢？", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道你想在某個日光正好的午後，在和我細細爭論過孰是孰非之後，再把你的槍刺入我的心臟？", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你回來了，我們共同跳了這支舞，這就夠了。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是以為，只要投入適當的火中，悲傷和仇恨也終將成為讓生活繼續的燃料。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "悲傷、仇恨……你還是承認了，拉芙希妮。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你的高尚終究還是害了你。你的火呢，拉芙希妮？", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不能就這樣將你的火毀去。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，你是說……城裡人？", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會死，但你的火焰應當在你的葬禮，你的還火儀式上熄滅，而不是現在。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，拉芙希妮，你早該讓滾燙的烈火驅散死亡，而不是費心攙扶逝者的手，訴說自己內心的糾結與悔恨，不然……", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你只會像現在這樣，錯失挽救一切的……最後的機會。", "name": "貪婪的紅龍"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$firestorm"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g11_castlecorridor_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_deathburning", "layer": 3.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高尚的紅龍驚愕地鬆開手，姐姐那並不比心臟被刺穿前更冰冷的身體落在地上。"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並非鮮血，而是紫火，從那貫穿身體的傷口咆哮著湧出，頃刻間充滿了整個長廊，流向整個堡壘……"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高尚的紅龍飛奔向陽台，而紫色的死火比她更快。"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g13_castlebalcony", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_deathburning", "layer": 3.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的火焰還來不及發出一點光芒，紫火就已經擴散開去，延燒到整座納斯爾紗。"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上次高尚的紅龍在這裡遠眺時，城裡的火焰還是星星點點。她再次進城時，紫火為城市鋪上了一層陰冷的底色。"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而現在……"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "納斯爾紗正熊熊燃燒，正如她見過的每一位不得安寧的死者。"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}